---

### âœ… Step 2: Initialize Git & Push to GitHub

#### Inside the folder in terminal:

```bash
git init
git add .
git commit -m "Initial Flask app commit"
git branch -M main
git remote add origin https://github.com/tushar19083/flask-app-github.git
git push -u origin main
------


Step 3: Verify
Go to your GitHub repo (e.g., https://github.com/tushar19083/flask-app-github)
You should see app.py, requirements.txt, and README.md files.
